{"tid":1594021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個民意撚，大家似乎忽略咗撤回後777民望冇起色，但要照樣落區帶比我哋嘅機會","createTime":"2019-09-25T10:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T11:11:21.000Z","uid":36592,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9c492e4c1e7bb65931542071c02bc5c3d6a2335b","tid":1594021,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首先，民意係維持呢場運動嘅最大力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n777當初撤回嘅如意算盤係要中立派同和理非收貨，然後孤立勇武派將佢哋一網打盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yEArL9L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyEArL9L.png&h=b91684d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但最新一次民調顯示，撤回後兩星期，777嘅民望係冇升過，民意並冇逆轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n777落區嘅目的除咗show，就係要拉攏中立派同和理非，希望民意慢慢扭轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都記得有個post講鬼佬教授話我哋曾經很多攻勢，而家只沉迷每週和警察打鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家777民望冇起色下同官員落區，正正係絕好機會比我哋對準政權，比和理非出場打民意戰，為運動帶嚟新方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於777落區一定極多狗，勇武手足可以保存實力，相反和理非有大把嘢可以做，比世界知道我哋有唔同抗爭手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 入場發言堅持五大訴求以理服眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 喺會場附近搞活動集會，播放黑警暴力片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 喺會場出面做人鏈，管弦樂團合唱榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 將黑警暴力同義士受傷圖片印A0 Size，喺會場出面示眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 大量流動連儂人出動搶鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n大家記得616點解會有200萬人出嚟，係因為777前一日開記招串柒柒激起民憤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n換言之，每次777出嚟都一定會講錯嘢，唔使勇武以身犯險，只要和理非落區展示力量，keep住民意就可以令呢場運動繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家繼續打民意戰，落區用和理非手段狙擊777同港共狗官，直到佢哋敗走社區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339277f32b8235eb7218596f89c8c7306e79b161","tid":1594021,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:48:15.000Z","msg":"繼續民意戰，派傳單，放映會，連儂牆，記者會，air drop，長輩圖，網上文宣，電台phone-in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.15752-9/71032141_436999597161608_2314460732244099072_n.png?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_eui2=AeG0iU4ikRoys3ftyyG2SoWpfGDlxWAFfpE6Lwffxq9D1zZIfC5YmMyGVxfyMVRIFUeZtXKXcn8uWdyLrcUD2OnT8hpL-9mGZp_oxUiHb7zxOQ&amp;_nc_oc=AQkCVDA252RWAGGiMHKz3wQ1S0Rdz1XyWiEGxKGp2BsSfb7iu7ce7hkxS77Aa758voI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=4f97db6b6b2dab932a6bb484a13e6c68&amp;oe=5DF834D3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.15752-9%2F71032141_436999597161608_2314460732244099072_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_eui2%3DAeG0iU4ikRoys3ftyyG2SoWpfGDlxWAFfpE6Lwffxq9D1zZIfC5YmMyGVxfyMVRIFUeZtXKXcn8uWdyLrcUD2OnT8hpL-9mGZp_oxUiHb7zxOQ%26_nc_oc%3DAQkCVDA252RWAGGiMHKz3wQ1S0Rdz1XyWiEGxKGp2BsSfb7iu7ce7hkxS77Aa758voI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D4f97db6b6b2dab932a6bb484a13e6c68%26oe%3D5DF834D3&h=982b9bf6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e10403a69edba5d49c4aa2587fdff63a77f34264","tid":1594021,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登各重要post整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/IRrY8V1N/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%ADlihkg-portal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2FIRrY8V1N%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25ADlihkg-portal&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTrHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=a4442486\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/IRrY8V1N/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%ADlihkg-portal</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全世界行動前一定要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n你地仲係唔肯改依啲壞習慣 只會愈黎愈多手足比人拉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589431\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589431</a>"},{"pid":"edc3577fa4ed72466f3c4e4dde1c6e9becb60220","tid":1594021,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190819/large/1566144504_94d2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190819%2Flarge%2F1566144504_94d2.gif&h=fb7823b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b3d7f85691b024903e91311a3a0fd0243e93510","tid":1594021,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:53:51.000Z","msg":"梁繼平義士：黑夜可以奪走我們眼中的光明，但無法熄滅我們心裡的火種。我們心裡作難，卻不要絕望；四面受敵，卻不要被困住。就如無人預計到反送中運動能在雨傘的灰燼中爆發，我們對公義自由的渴求亦不會停止，抗爭運動的星火終有一日燎原。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365bf24c1d8a55ecd193e46d484876ac19b0155e","tid":1594021,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime